headline: Synchrony Announces Quarterly Common Stock Dividend of $0.30 Per Share
summary: Synchrony Financial (NYSE: SYF) announced today that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.30 per share of common stock, payable on November 17, 2025, to holders of record at the close of business on November 5, 2025.
